<p>I am building an AngularJS application and i need to store data which is inside the p tags into local storage. The challenge is that ng-model cannot be associated with p tags. Example</p>  <pre><code>&lt;div class="row"&gt;     &lt;div class="col"&gt;         &lt;p&gt;{{product.ID}}&lt;/p&gt;         &lt;p&gt;{{product.title}}&lt;/p&gt;         &lt;button ng-click="addItem()"&gt;Add to Cart&lt;/button&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>  <p>I have a list products and i am displaying it through ng-repeat and i want to store the product.ID and product.title of the product whose corresponding Add to Cart button is clicked.</p>